PrecisAppointment of KIM PERRY BUTLER as Consul General of Canada at Minneapolis, United States of America; HECTOR LLEWELLYN COWAN as Consul General of Canada at St. Petersburg, Russian Federation; PAUL DUBOIS as Ambassador of Canada to the Federal Republic of Germany; ALAIN DUDOIT as Consul General of Canada at Los Angeles, United States of America; MICHAEL FINE as Consul General of Canada at Denver, United States of America; BARBARA GIBSON as Ambassador and Permanent Representative of Canada to the Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe; FREDERICKA GREGORY as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Denmark; PING M. MARCHAND as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Senegal; PHILIP MacKINNON as Ambassador of Canada to the Arab Republic of Egypt; BRIAN OAK as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Ecuador; JEFFREY N. PARKER as Consul General of Canada at Seattle, United States of America; DONALD SMITH as Ambassador of Canada to the Holy See; DON STEPHENSON as Permanent Representative and Ambassador of Canada to the Office of the United Nations and to the World Trade Organization; ALAN VIRTUE as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Singapore; SANDELLE SCRIMSHAW as High Commissioner of Canada to the Kingdom of Lesotho and to the Kingdom of Swaziland; and JAMES LAMBERT as High Commissioner to Belize.
